[68.424198, "o", "input: 2727 bp\r\negfp: 717 bp\r\nflag: 90 bp\r\nsnap: 549 bp\r\noutput: 3591 bp\r\n\r\negfp starts at position 210 in output\r\nsnap ends at position 1554 in output\r\n\r\nBefore egfp (input): ...tttaagaaggagatatacat\r\negfp start: atgagcaagggcgaggagct...\r\n"]
