[148.820129, "o", "snap starts with: atggacaaagactgcgaaatgaagcgcacc...\r\nsnap ends with: ...cacagactgggtaagcctgggctgggttaa\r\nsnap length: 549 bp\r\n\r\n\r\nIn output at position 210:\r\n  atgagcaagggcgaggagctgttcaccggg... (should be egfp start)\r\n\r\nAt position 924:\r\n  ggtagtggctccggtagcggtagcggcagc\r\n\r\nCompare with egfp[714:] = taa\r\n\r\nSo egfp in output is: output[210:924]\r\n  Last 30 bp: ...atcactctcggcatggacgagctgtacaaa\r\n  Compare to egfp[684:714]: atcactctcggcatggacgagctgtacaaa\r\n\r\nAfter egfp at position 924:\r\n  ggtagtggctccggtagcggtagcggcagc\r\n\r\nDoes flag start here?"]
