[172.802271, "o", "  Ends with: ...tccggttctggttcaggtagtggttcataa\r\n\r\nsnap without start codon: 546 bp\r\n  Starts with: gacaaagactgcgaaatgaagcgcaccacc...\r\n  Ends with: ...cacagactgggtaagcctgggctgggttaa\r\n\r\n=== Checking in output ===\r\n\r\negfp (no stop) should be at output[210:924]\r\n  ✓ egfp matches!\r\n\r\nflag (no start) should be at output[924:1011]"]
[172.802534, "o", "\r\n  ✗ flag doesn't match\r\n\r\n=== SUMMARY ===\r\nExpected structure in output:\r\n  Position 210: start of egfp (without stop codon)\r\n  Position 924: start of flag (without start codon)\r\n  Position 1011: start of snap (check if with or without start codon)\r\n"]
