[391.762996, "o", "SNAP primers:\r\n  Forward template binding: GACAAAGACTGCGAAATGAA (20 bp)\r\n    Tm = 58.25°C\r\n  Reverse template binding: TTAACCCAGCCCAGGC (16 bp)\r\n    Tm = 60.27°C\r\n  ΔTm = 2.02°C\r\n"]
[391.763285, "o", "  Requirements: PASS\r\n    Length 15-45bp: ✓\r\n    Tm 58-72°C: ✓\r\n    ΔTm ≤ 5°C: ✓\r\n\r\n"]
