[421.75927, "o", "=== GOLDEN GATE ASSEMBLY VERIFICATION ===\r\n\r\nOverhangs in primers:\r\n  egfp_fwd: ATGA (will be on 5' end of PCR product)\r\n  egfp_rev: TACC (will be on 5' end of PCR product, RC on 3' end)\r\n  flag_fwd: GGTA (will be on 5' end of PCR product)\r\n  flag_rev: TGAA (will be on 5' end of PCR product, RC on 3' end)\r\n"]
[421.759557, "o", "  input_fwd: TGAG (will be on 5' end of PCR product)\r\n  input_rev: TCAT (will be on 5' end of PCR product, RC on 3' end)\r\n  snap_fwd: GACA (will be on 5' end of PCR product)\r\n  snap_rev: CTCA (will be on 5' end of PCR product, RC on 3' end)\r\n\r\nExpected assembly order and junctions:\r\n  1. input backbone\r\n     3' overhang: TCAT -> will ligate to ATGA\r\n  2. egfp (no stop)\r\n     5' overhang: ATGA\r\n     3' overhang: TACC -> will ligate to GGTA\r\n  3. flag (no start/stop)\r\n     5' overhang: GGTA\r\n     3' overhang: TGAA -> will ligate to GACA\r\n  4. snap (no start)\r\n     5' overhang: GACA\r\n     3' overhang: CTCA -> will ligate to TGAG\r\n  -> back to input backbone\r\n     5' overhang: TGAG\r\n\r\n✓ Assembly design is correct for circular plasmid formation!\r\n"]
